Technology billionaire Elon Musk pursued a sale of struggling electric-car company Tesla to Google in 2013 , according to an excerpt of a book published .
Beset by technical problems on its flagship Model S , Tesla in early 2013 was on the verge of bankruptcy .
Musk proposed that Google buy Tesla for $ 6 billion and factory expansions .
Tesla 's fortunes changed in May 2013 when the company reported a third-generation car .